Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,120)}O月X日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,160)}我感覺自己是被愛著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,200)}他們所搬出來的特別套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,240)}讓我大快朵頤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,280)}除此之外還有什麼好要求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,320)}的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,360)}我真實感受到昔日的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,400)}世界充滿了美妙的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,440)}這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,480)}送出來的酒也是五花八門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.82,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(10,520)}每天都在品嘗美酒
